---
// ===================== MARKETING & SALES STRATEGY =====================
import { homePhotos } from '../../data/home';
---

<section class="section-pad mktg" id="marketing" data-screen-label="Marketing experts">
  <img class="mktg__bg" src={homePhotos['pool']} alt="" />
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="mktg__top reveal">
      <div class="mktg__intro">
        <p class="eyebrow">Marketing &amp; sales strategy</p>
        <h2>How we beat the market.</h2>
        <p class="lede muted">Hyper focused marketing campaigns, exclusively for short term rentals, that extend way beyond just posting on Airbnb and Vrbo. This is true marketing. Targeted ads, reaching your primary customer before they book, with sales professionals who close leads, for direct bookings that earn you more money.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="mktg__cta">
        <h3>Surpass the competition today</h3>
        <p>Cardo homes outperform the market average by up to 35%+</p>
        <a href="#estimate" class="btn btn-lg btn-blk btn-round">Get my free earning estimate</a>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <div class="mktg__caps reveal">
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Exclusive travel-agency partnerships</h3><p>Direct relationships with top travel agencies and OTAs put your home in front of high-intent, high-value travelers other managers can't reach.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Airbnb Superhost &amp; VRBO Premier status</h3><p>Top-tier host status on both platforms boosts your ranking, badges, and guest trust — so your listing wins the click and the booking.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Insurance agency partnerships</h3><p>Relationships with specialist short-term-rental insurers mean the right coverage for your home and your guests, arranged and kept current for you.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Decor-first content</h3><p>Our in-house design team styles the home before the shoot, so every room photographs like an editorial spread — and books at a premium.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Editorial photography &amp; video</h3><p>A dedicated content shoot builds a full library of images and lifestyle video — fuel for your listing, website, ads, and socials.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Always-on social media</h3><p>Managed Instagram and Pinterest: keyword-optimized reels, carousels, and pins that keep your home in front of future guests every month.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Travel-influencer campaigns</h3><p>Paid and trade collaborations with vetted travel creators who stay and film — reels that put your home in front of thousands of new travelers.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Paid ads &amp; retargeting</h3><p>We turn the strongest content into targeted PPC campaigns aimed at high-intent traveler personas and drive them straight to your booking page.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Airbnb listing SEO</h3><p>Keyword research and monthly listing optimization — with direct access to an Airbnb Senior Market Manager — to rank where your highest-paying guests search.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Direct-booking website</h3><p>A branded site wired to your live calendar: instant credibility on a name search and a dedicated landing page for every ad we run.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Realtor referral network</h3><p>A referral network of San Diego agents feeding high-value owner leads and warm introductions to new doors across the county.</p></div>
      <div class="mcap"><h3>Past-guest email funnel</h3><p>Targeted email campaigns to our list of past guests, bringing repeat direct bookings on demand — the audience that already loves a Cardo stay.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
